tags.name: Brendan Simbwaye Road
tags.note: The Namibian (2021-12-21): "The multi-million-dollar 52-kilometre Namalubi-Isize-Luhonono road in the Kabbe North constituency was renamed in honour of the late liberation struggle hero Brendan Simbwaye."
